episodes.title: Case #20 - Jason Duncan (Cult Therapy)
episodes.description: Rootless Coffee Presents- Dossier: Jason Duncan, our subject for this evening's interrogation, has survived Christian Cults, an abusive step-parent, addiction in a biological parent, being a Southern Baptist, and growing up completely surrounded by the other. Conversely, he ws othered due to it all. This is truly a special interview. A tale of haunting like no other, told to your 3:33 AM agents Nathaniel and Peter over a mason jar of black, steaming Rootless Coffee. if you wish to catch the spirits appropriately, head on over to https://www.rootlesscoffee.com and enter SHADOW20 at checkout for a 20 percent savings! Rootless, they roast stuff, so drink it!
